                     <td>
                        <h1>Campaign Valyan's Heirs</h1>(home page: <a href="http://www.lore-merchant.org" target="_blank">www.lore-merchant.org</a>)<br></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                     <td><span class="body"><i>East of the Caucavic Mountains lies a large expanse of grasslands. The villages of this area are mostly descended from a single
                              kaer that owes its survival to the Troubadour hero Valyan. Every year, a group of newly initiated adepts is pledged to the
                              service of these villages. These adepts are collectively known as Valyan's Heirs... *(This is an active campaign, and is not
                              accepting associations on characters.)*</i></span></td>
                  </tr>
